<Layout
  title="📊 Data Taiwan — Understanding an Island Through Numbers"
  description="Taiwan's enterprise landscape, SVG resources, open data platforms, civic tech tools, and digital democracy resources"
>
  <div class="data-page">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Hero -->
      <section class="hero">
        <h1 class="hero-title">📊 Data Taiwan — Understanding an Island Through Numbers</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          From enterprise powerhouses to open data platforms — explore Taiwan through curated data storytelling
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Act 2: Enterprise Landscape -->
      <section class="enterprise-section">
        <article class="story-block">
          <h2 class="story-title">🏢 Enterprise Landscape — How Does One Country Power the Global Supply Chain?</h2>
          <p>
            Taiwan punches far above its weight in the global economy. This country of 23 million people produces over 60% of the world's semiconductors, 
            92% of the most advanced chips, and houses the supply chain nerve center for everything from iPhones to Tesla vehicles.
          </p>
          <p>
            The interactive bubble chart below reveals Taiwan's economic DNA — where <strong>TSMC alone represents 39% of Taiwan's total market capitalization</strong>, 
            equivalent to the combined value of two-thirds of all other listed companies. Behind the "Silicon Shield" narrative lies a concentrated ecosystem 
            of precision manufacturing, from Foxconn's massive electronics assembly to ASE's semiconductor packaging empire.
          </p>
          <p>Bubble size represents market cap; color indicates sector. Drag to explore, filter by industry, or toggle between market cap/revenue/employee count.</p>
        </article>

        <div class="controls">
          <div class="size-toggle">
            <label>Bubble size by:</label>
            <button class="toggle-btn active" data-mode="marketCap">Market Cap</button>
            <button class="toggle-btn" data-mode="revenue">Revenue</button>
            <button class="toggle-btn" data-mode="employees">Employees</button>
          </div>
          <div class="sector-filters">
            <button class="sector-btn active" data-sector="all">All</button>
            {sectors.map(s => (
              <button
                class="sector-btn"
                data-sector={s}
                style={`--sector-color: ${sectorColors[s] || '#888'}`}
              >
                <span class="sector-dot" style={`background: ${sectorColors[s] || '#888'}`}></span>
                {s}
              </button>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="bubble-chart"></div>

        <div class="insights">
          <h3>🔍 Key Insights</h3>
          <div class="insight-grid">
            <div class="insight-card">
              <div class="insight-number">39%</div>
              <div class="insight-label">TSMC's share of Taiwan's total market cap</div>
              <div class="insight-detail">One company ≈ 2/3 of 1,000+ other listed companies</div>
            </div>
            <div class="insight-card">
              <div class="insight-number">72%</div>
              <div class="insight-label">Top 50 companies' share of total market cap</div>
              <div class="insight-detail">Taiwan's stock market highly concentrated in large enterprises</div>
            </div>
            <div class="insight-card">
              <div class="insight-number">12</div>
              <div class="insight-label">Semiconductor-related companies in top 50</div>
              <div class="insight-detail">Cementing the "Silicon Shield" — semiconductors are Taiwan's national defense</div>
            </div>
            <div class="insight-card">
              <div class="insight-number">9</div>
              <div class="insight-label">Financial institutions in top 50</div>
              <div class="insight-detail">Post-consolidation, financial sector provides stability</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-link">
          <a href="/economy" class="btn-action">View full ranking →</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Act 3: The Shape of Taiwan -->
      <section class="svg-section">
        <article class="story-block">
          <h2 class="story-title">🗺️ The Shape of Taiwan — AI Can't Draw Taiwan Correctly. Here's the Real Version.</h2>
          <p>
            Most AI image generation models lack structured geographic data for Taiwan in their training sets. 
            The result: AI-generated images of Taiwan are often distorted, disproportionate, or confused with other islands.
          </p>
          <p>
            Taiwan.md provides <strong>accurate, open-source, freely usable</strong> SVG outlines — a definitive answer 
            for every scenario that needs to know "what does Taiwan look like."
          </p>
        </article>

        <div class="svg-grid">
          <div class="svg-card">
            <div class="svg-preview">
              <img src="/assets/svg/taiwan-icon-wiki.svg" alt="Taiwan Icon" />
            </div>
            <div class="svg-info">
              <h4>taiwan-icon.svg</h4>
              <p class="svg-desc">Simple outline — Best for icons, logos, small sizes</p>
              <div class="svg-actions">
                <a href="/assets/svg/taiwan-icon-wiki.svg" download class="btn-svg">Download</a>
                <button class="btn-svg" onclick="copySVG('taiwan-icon-wiki.svg', this)">Copy SVG</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="svg-card">
